# This directory holds pre-computed text embeddings from compute_embeddings.py.
# All generated JSON files are gitignored — only this .gitkeep is committed.
#
# Files produced by compute_embeddings.py:
#   startups.json   — { startup_id: [384 floats], ... }
#   investors.json  — { investor_id: [384 floats], ... }
#   _metadata.json  — model name, dim, versions, fields_used, generated_at
#
# Regenerate with:
#   npm run embeddings:synthetic-matches
#   (or)
#   npm run prepare:synthetic-matches   (embeddings + pairs + training)
#
# NOTICE: Embeddings are SYNTHETIC and EXPERIMENTAL.
# They represent text similarity for profile-fit matching only.
# They are NOT investment advice and do NOT predict startup success.
